1. *Lale* su cvetale u parku. (Lilies were blooming in the park.)
2. Volim da mirišem *lale*. (I love to smell lilies.)
3. Ona je posadila nekoliko *lala* u bašti. (She planted a few lilies in the garden.)
4. Kupila je buket *lala* za svoju majku. (She bought a bouquet of lilies for her mother.)
5. *Lale* su omiljeni cvet mnogim ljudima. (Lilies are a favorite flower for many people.)
6. U dvorištu su bile posađene bele *lale*. (White lilies were planted in the courtyard.)
7. Deca su skupljala *lale* po livadi. (Children were picking lilies in the meadow.)
8. *Lale* se često koriste u aranžmanima za venčanja. (Lilies are often used in wedding arrangements.)
9. U prodavnici su bili dostupni različiti tipovi *lala*. (Different types of lilies were available in the store.)
10. Njegova slika je bila ukrašena crvenim *lalama*. (His picture was decorated with red lilies.)